				.wrapper
					p Friday, August 22nd 2014 at 8 PM EDT time
					p Online event only at this page

					//- failure
					p Due to recording error during the original presentation at the Cryptolina Expo 2014, Phil Champagne will be re-presenting his talk online for anyone to watch. There will be a Q&amp;A session at the end.

					p The presentation will discuss a theoretical strategy to implement a sidechain utilisation without any modification of the Bitcoin software protocol. This type of sidechain could have major implications for the expansion of the blockchain beyond the recording of currency transactions.  It will open up a vast array of application for new business opportunities and innovative tools and services to explore.

					p We would like to invite all developers interested to participate in the implementation of this project and entrepreneurs interested by all the consequent social implications to watch to this presentation.

